<header>
  <h1>ALTITUDE</h1>
  <p>Where music rises above time. A one-day, multi‑era festival celebrating legends, icons, and the future of sound.</p>
</header>

<section id="about">
  <h2>Festival Overview</h2>
  <p><span class="highlight">Location:</span> Miami Beach Bandshell, Miami, FL</p>
  <p><span class="highlight">Date:</span> One-Day Festival</p>
  <p><span class="highlight">Experience:</span> Oceanfront views, immersive sound, iconic performances, and a crowd united by music across generations.</p>
</section>

<section id="vision">
  <h2>Festival Vision</h2>
  <p><strong>Altitude</strong> exists to show how music evolves while staying emotionally timeless. From classic rock and soul to hip‑hop and modern pop, the festival honors artists who changed the culture and inspired the next generation.</p>
  <p>We center voices that pushed boundaries, broke rules, and shaped the sound of their era. When fans leave, we want them feeling connected — not just to music, but to its history and future.</p>
</section>

